you everything that I did.

00:14:29.295 --> 00:14:34.603 position:5% line:77% align:start
Because you can understand now;
You can appreciate what kind of
father Naoyuki was.

00:14:38.708 --> 00:14:42.546 position:7% line:83% align:start
[TOMOYA] He'd come home on his
break and bring me candy.

00:14:42.546 --> 00:14:46.685 position:13% line:83% align:start
