we'd go on walks together.

00:14:46.685 --> 00:14:49.990 position:21% line:83% align:start
It's sad how easily
I forgot all that.

00:14:49.990 --> 00:14:52.692 position:13% line:83% align:start
Tomoya, even though I know
you're not fond of Naoyuki,

00:14:52.692 --> 00:14:56.297 position:21% line:83% align:start
do you think he's a
failure as a father?

00:14:56.297 --> 00:14:57.933 position:33% line:89% align:start
Not really.

00:14:57.933 --> 00:15:01.671 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm a bigger failure as a person
than he ever was as a father.

00:15:01.671 --> 00:15:05.576 position:7% line:83% align:start
Right now, I'm standing in the
same place that my dad did.

00:15:05.576 --> 00:15:08.180 position:5% line:89% align:start
But I don't feel like fighting.

00:15:08.180 --> 00:15:10.615 position:19% line:89% align:start
I feel like giving up.

00:15:10.615 --> 00:15:13.086 position:13% line:83% align:start
All I can think of is how
weak and pathetic I am.

00:15:13.086 --> 00:15:17.591 position:35% line:83% align:start
[chuckles]
You're not unlike him, you know.

00:15:17.591 --> 00:15:21.864 position:7% line:83% align:start
I think he's weak and pathetic
in his own way, as well.

00:15:21.864 --> 00:15:28.306 position:5% line:77% align:start
But even if he wasn't perfect, I
know he worked hard and did
everything he could for you.

00:15:28.306 --> 00:15:33.011 position:5% line:77% align:start
For that reason, no matter what
happens, I'll always be proud of
him.

00:15:33.011 --> 00:15:36.783 position:7% line:83% align:start
As a man, my son may have his
fair share of short comings,

00:15:36.783 --> 00:15:40.989 position:5% line:83% align:start
but as a father, I truly believe
that he did a good job.

00:15:42.090 --> 00:15:43.892 position:30% line:89% align:start
[TOMOYA] I...

00:15:44.894 --> 00:15:46.929 position:27% line:89% align:start
I think so too.

00:15:46.929 --> 00:15:49.867 position:16% line:83% align:start
And there's nothing more
I could ask for.

00:15:51.002 --> 00:15:55.241 position:13% line:83% align:start
[SHINO] Thank you so much
for saying that.

00:15:55.241 --> 00:15:57.344 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Shino chuckles]

00:15:57.344 --> 00:16:00.146 position:7% line:89% align:start
Oh, this such a relief for me.

00:16:06.655 --> 00:16:09.993 position:16% line:83% align:start
Tomoya, your father has
worked too hard.

00:16:11.295 --> 00:16:14.332 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's time for him to take
a well-deserved break.

00:16:14.332 --> 00:16:16.902 position:21% line:83% align:start
Please tell him that
his job is done.

00:16:16.902 --> 00:16:20.606 position:10% line:83% align:start
Tell him that it's all right
to come home now.

00:16:20.606 --> 00:16:22.209 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'll be right here
waiting for him.

00:16:22.209 --> 00:16:26.147 position:13% line:83% align:start
There's no reason for him
to suffer anymore.

00:16:32.289 --> 00:16:34.358 position:27% line:89% align:start
[TOMOYA] Ushio!

00:16:34.358 --> 00:16:36.559 position:27% line:89% align:start
Did you find it?

00:16:37.795 --> 00:16:39.463 position:7% line:89% align:start
Oh, is that your little girl?

00:16:39.463 --> 00:16:42.068 position:16% line:89% align:start
Yeah, her name's Ushio.

00:16:48.943 --> 00:16:51.046 position:10% line:83% align:start
[TOMOYA] Were you searching
for it all this time?

00:16:51.046 --> 00:16:52.681 position:27% line:89% align:start
[USHIO] Uh-huh.

00:16:52.681 --> 00:16:54.684 position:24% line:89% align:start
[TOMOYA] I see...

00:17:01.726 --> 00:17:05.931 position:21% line:83% align:start
Ushio, I'm sorry to
have to say this,

00:17:05.931 --> 00:17:08.268 position:24% line:83% align:start
but we may not be
able to find it.

00:17:08.268 --> 00:17:09.703 position:7% line:89% align:start
We've done everything we can.

00:17:09.703 --> 00:17:13.241 position:16% line:83% align:start
All I can do now is buy
you a new one, okay?

00:17:16.511 --> 00:17:18.281 position:33% line:89% align:start
But that...

00:17:18.281 --> 00:17:20.451 position:13% line:89% align:start
But that was the only one.

00:17:20.451 --> 00:17:23.721 position:10% line:83% align:start
No, there was a whole bunch
of them at the store.

00:17:24.789 --> 00:17:26.591 position:24% line:83% align:start
But that's the one
you picked out.

00:17:26.591 --> 00:17:29.195 position:5% line:89% align:start
That's the robot you bought me.

00:17:31.198 --> 00:17:34.869 position:13% line:83% align:start
That was the first time...
Daddy.

