[TOMOYA] Ushio... [USHIO] Hm?

00:17:42.912 --> 00:17:45.149 position:38% line:83% align:start
[TOMOYA]
You've been lonely, huh?

00:17:45.149 --> 00:17:47.084 position:27% line:89% align:start
