okay if I stay with you?

00:18:15.288 --> 00:18:16.556 position:38% line:89% align:start
Mm-hmm.

00:18:16.556 --> 00:18:18.225 position:21% line:89% align:start
You really mean it?

00:18:18.225 --> 00:18:20.294 position:21% line:89% align:start
I want you to stay.

00:18:21.496 --> 00:18:23.398 position:21% line:89% align:start
[TOMOYA] Thank you.

00:18:23.398 --> 00:18:28.071 position:5% line:77% align:start
[USHIO] But... but I'm still sad
'cause I lost something I can't
get back.

00:18:30.107 --> 00:18:32.277 position:41% line:89% align:start
Daddy?

00:18:32.277 --> 00:18:34.079 position:41% line:89% align:start
Umm...

00:18:35.046 --> 00:18:37.183 position:27% line:89% align:start
[quiet sniffles]

00:18:38.084 --> 00:18:40.220 position:35% line:89% align:start
I don't...

00:18:40.220 --> 00:18:42.823 position:16% line:83% align:start
I don't have to hold it
in anymore, right?

00:18:42.823 --> 00:18:46.261 position:5% line:83% align:start
Just like you said on the train?
