00:19:27.248 --> 00:19:29.650 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm so sorry.

00:19:42.233 --> 00:19:44.603 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hey, Ushio.

00:19:44.603 --> 00:19:48.041 position:19% line:83% align:start
