Mommy if you'd like that.

00:19:48.041 --> 00:19:49.042 position:38% line:89% align:start
Mm-hmm.

00:19:49.042 --> 00:19:52.046 position:7% line:89% align:start
Okay then, come sit over here.

00:20:00.023 --> 00:20:04.028 position:16% line:89% align:start
Now, where do I start...

00:20:04.028 --> 00:20:08.634 position:7% line:77% align:start
Back in high school, Mommy was
having a tough time, so she
cried a lot.

00:20:08.634 --> 00:20:10.504 position:5% line:89% align:start
That was back when we first met.

00:20:10.504 --> 00:20:12.806 position:19% line:83% align:start
She didn't believe in
herself very much.

00:20:12.806 --> 00:20:16.579 position:7% line:77% align:start
I remember she was standing at
the bottom of the hill at our
high school.

00:20:16.579 --> 00:20:19.848 position:10% line:77% align:start
And do you know what she did
while she was standing there
that morning?

00:20:19.848 --> 00:20:23.153 position:21% line:83% align:start
She closed her eyes
and she said "anpan."

00:20:23.153 --> 00:20:25.556 position:19% line:83% align:start
That was a funny habit
Mommy had.

00:20:25.556 --> 00:20:28.627 position:7% line:77% align:start
