with work and didn't have time
to make lunch for Mommy.

00:20:34.702 --> 00:20:38.406 position:7% line:83% align:start
Of course, Mommy would've been
happy if she had Sanae's food,

00:20:38.406 --> 00:20:41.309 position:13% line:83% align:start
and maybe Sanae could make
time if she had to,

00:20:41.309 --> 00:20:45.014 position:19% line:83% align:start
but Mommy was too nice
to ask her.

00:20:45.014 --> 00:20:47.751 position:5% line:83% align:start
That's what your Mommy was like;
Really sweet.

00:20:47.751 --> 00:20:49.954 position:16% line:89% align:start
Let's see, what else...

00:20:53.292 --> 00:20:55.127 position:30% line:89% align:start
Uh, she, uh...

00:20:55.127 --> 00:20:57.831 position:24% line:89% align:start
Ah, your mommy...

00:20:59.267 --> 00:21:01.068 position:33% line:89% align:start
Mommy was...

00:21:08.845 --> 00:21:10.848 position:35% line:89% align:start
Nagisa...

00:21:11.750 --> 00:21:13.551 position:35% line:89% align:start
Nagisa...

00:21:16.489 --> 00:21:18.291 position:35% line:89% align:start
Nagisa...

00:21:22.162 --> 00:21:24.866 position:38% line:89% align:start
Daddy...

00:21:24.866 --> 00:21:28.003 position:7% line:89% align:start
Silly, why are you crying too?

00:21:28.871 --> 00:21:30.839 position:16% line:89% align:start
Sorry, it's nothing bad.

00:21:30.839 --> 00:21:33.109 position:7% line:89% align:start
I was just thinking of Mommy.

00:21:39.017 --> 00:21:41.921 position:21% line:83% align:start
Okay, let's get back
to the story.

00:21:41.921 --> 00:21:45.959 position:7% line:77% align:start
