[TOMOYA] <i>Nagisa,</i>
 <i>I found it.</i>

00:21:52.803 --> 00:21:55.072 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>I finally found it.</i>

00:21:55.072 --> 00:21:57.475 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Something only</i>
 <i>I can protect.</i>

00:21:57.475 --> 00:22:01.146 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>A precious treasure that</i>
 <i>only I can protect.</i>

00:22:01.146 --> 00:22:03.215 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>It was right here.</i>

00:22:06.152 --> 00:22:10.191 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Right in front of</i>
 <i>me, all along.</i>

